OL,6,FITV Granada Reports journalist visits
OL,7,Fthe station to find out how they are
OL,8,Fdementia friendly.
OL,10,FA radio station that hopes to take
OL,11,Fpeople living with dementia back to
OL,12,Fthe "happier times in their lives"
OL,13,Fthrough music, has been given a
OL,14,Fcommunity radio licence by OFCOM.
OL,16,FDementia Friendly Radio can broadcast
OL,17,Fon DAB for the first since its
OL,18,Finternet launch in 2020, becoming the
OL,19,Ffirst dementia-friendly Digital Audio
OL,20,FBroadcasting station in the UK.
