OL,3,CA dementia friendly radio station is
OL,4,Cgiven broadcast licence
OL,6,F"Most of what we do is provide
OL,7,Freminiscent resources for people, so
OL,8,Fthings that can illicit nostalgia, can
OL,9,Ftake people back to happier times in
OL,10,Ftheir lives, so it's music from
OL,11,Fcertain eras.
OL,13,F"We tend to stick to music from the
OL,14,F40s to the 80s, because that will
OL,15,Foften be the time in people's lives
OL,16,Fwhen they've made the strongest
OL,17,Fconnection to music."
