OL,6,FThe station also provides reality
OL,7,Forientation for listeners, which is a
OL,8,Ftechnique that integrates time and day
OL,9,Finto conversation with people who have
OL,10,Fdementia.
OL,12,FNat added: "We try and make it so that
OL,13,Fwhen we're speaking to people through
OL,14,Fthe broadcast, it is a bit more
OL,15,Fconversation and friendly rather than
OL,16,Ftalking at them and telling them what
OL,17,Fto do, we try to make it more gentle.
