OL,6,F"When people are leaving our radio
OL,7,Fstation on for loved ones, they're
OL,8,Ftrusting us to sit with them and to be
OL,9,Falone with them, so we like to be
OL,10,Ffriendly company for them.
OL,12,F"It can often make people feel like
OL,13,Fthey're cared for or that they have
OL,14,Fcompany when there's a friendly voice."
