OL,6,FTo be more accessible to dementia
OL,7,Flisteners, the station does not
OL,8,Finclude adverts in their content. A
OL,9,Fhas been created to raise money for
OL,10,Fthe equipment needed for the
OL,11,Ftransition to broadcast. More than
OL,12,F#2,500 has been raised so far.
OL,14,FRebecca Anderson, Managing Director at
OL,15,FRemember Me, a residential that
OL,16,Fprovides dementia care in , says the
OL,17,Fstation is beneficial to residents.
OL,19,FShe said: "Music in general just makes
OL,20,Feveryone happier, it takes everyone
OL,21,Fback so it's nostalgic for them.
